# Mobile UI Components

## Gluestack UI

**Use Gluestack components instead of React Native core:**

| Instead of | Use |
|---|---|
| `View` | `Box` |
| `TouchableOpacity` | `Pressable` |
| `Text` (RN) | `Text` (from `@gluestack-ui/themed`) |
| Custom buttons | `Button` + `ButtonText` |
| Manual layouts | `VStack`, `HStack` with `space` prop |
| Custom cards | `Card` |

