## Design System Constants

From `constants/Styles.ts`:

```typescript
import { TextStyles, Spacing, BorderRadius } from '@/constants/Styles';

// Spacing: xs=4, sm=8, md=16, lg=24, xl=32, xxl=48
// BorderRadius: sm=4, md=8, lg=12, xl=16, xxl=24
// TextStyles: title(24/bold), subtitle(18/semibold), body(16), caption(14), small(12), label(14/medium)
```

## Component Patterns

- **Text:** Use `<ThemedText type="title|subtitle|default|caption">` for automatic theming
- **Views:** Use `<ThemedView>` for themed containers
- **Buttons:** Use `<ButtonWithLoading variant="solid|outline|link" size="xs|sm|md|lg|xl">`
- **Styles:** Use `StyleSheet.create()` with design system constants, never inline hardcoded values
- **Colors:** Import from `constants/Colors.ts`, access via `Colors[colorScheme ?? 'light']`

## Style Organization

```typescript
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: { flex: 1, padding: Spacing.md },
  title: { ...TextStyles.title, marginBottom: Spacing.md },
});
```
